{"id":174275,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/08/译者-《译者》每日原文推荐-2011825/","date":"2011-08-26T04:00:19Z","modified":"2011-08-26T05:34:22Z","title":"译者 | 《译者》每日原文推荐  2011/8/25","content":"<p><p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以下为每日原文推荐。如果你有兴趣，请参与翻译并将译文寄给</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《译者》</span></a><b>(</b></span><span><b><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"mailto:iyizhe@gmail.com\"><span>iyizhe@gmail.com</span></a>)</span></b></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以便与大家共享。欢迎使用</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify?uri=yizhe&#038;loc=en_US\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">邮件组</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/f1NDK\">Google Reader</a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和推特（</span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/yigroup\">@yigroup</a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/xiaomi2020\">@xiaomi2020</a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）跟踪我们的最新消息。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【时政热点】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国数字时代：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/2011/08/liang-shuxin-%E6%A2%81%E6%A0%91%E6%96%B0-independent-candidate-disqualified-from-preliminary-round/?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+chinadigitaltimes%2FbKzO+%28China+Digital+Times+%28CDT%29%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的独立候选人梁树新未能通过提名</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——公民参与立法程序的努力再次受挫</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2011/aug/25/china-truck-driver-executed-mongolian-herder\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国处死引发内蒙牧民骚乱的卡车司机</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20110825/ap_on_re_as/as_china_tibet\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国换下西藏的强硬派党委书记</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——来自河南的陈全国换下了原书记张庆黎，官方没有解释原因</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20110825/ap_on_re_as/as_china_migrant_schools\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">北京关闭民工子弟学校，孩子上学成问题</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——都是户口惹得祸</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>Granta</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.granta.com/Online-Only/1911-The-Other-Revolution\">1911<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，另一场革命</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——今年中国有两个历史性的大事应该纪念，一个是中共成立</span></span><span><span>90</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">周年，一个是辛亥革命百年。后者注定将要无声无息地过去。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">东亚论坛：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.eastasiaforum.org/2011/08/25/whos-afraid-of-chinas-middle-class/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">谁惧怕中国的中产阶级？</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——西方认为中国的中产阶级是变革的力量，中国当权者则把他们看作是稳定的力量。到底谁是对的呢？</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《每日电讯报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/china-business/8720097/The-Chinese-are-patriotically-shopping-til-they-drop.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国消费者的爱国情结</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——新中国成立之后，中国人民在爱国主义、民族主义的宣传中做出了很大牺牲</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20110825/ap_on_re_as/as_china_mine_flood\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国非法煤窑发生透水，</span>26<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">名矿工失踪</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——黑龙江七台河一处非法煤窑透水已两天</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国听说博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.chinahearsay.com/greenpeace-textile-chemical-may-cause-male-fish-tits/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">绿色和平组织称长江里的纺织化工品污染可能导致雄鱼长出乳头</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/environment/2011/aug/25/wikileaks-fears-china-nuclear-safety\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">维基解密电报揭示出对中国核安全的担心</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——新披露的文件显示出核电站合同竞标的保密性、以及中国核电管理和监控的潜在弱点</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》</span></span><span><span>“</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">北京奥运会办得很棒，不过后遗症也不轻。</span></span><span><span>”</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">部分由于政府提高利率，</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-08-25/beijing-olympics-bill-due-as-record-bonds-mature-china-credit.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">北京的</span>15<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">家政府金融机构明年将面临创纪录的</span>162<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">亿元人民币还款</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">（含利息）</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/08/25/world/asia/25china.html?_r=1\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国重新调整经济平衡的努力面临障碍</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“中国领导人缺乏实施广泛经济结构调整的政治动力和紧迫感”</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/environment/2011/aug/25/conocophillips-china-oil-spill\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">康菲公司曾警告说中方合作伙伴会阻碍清理泄漏的原油</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——据维基解密披露出来的美国使馆电文透露，康菲公司在四年前就警告说，中海油坚持要雇用自己下属企业承担油污清理任务，而这可能会耽误事。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">彭博新闻：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-24/china-oceanic-authority-prepares-to-sue-for-spill-compensation.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国准备对康菲和中海油的漏油事件提起诉讼</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——据康菲公司透露，大约</span></span><span><span>3200</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">桶原油和钻探油液泄露到渤海中。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社分析：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/nm/20110825/bs_nm/us_china_patents\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国通讯业专利猛增，预示着创新时代的来临</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国的中兴和华为两家公司去年分列世界国际专利申请数量的第二和第四名</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《每日电讯报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/science/space/8722806/As-China-gazes-upwards-watch-this-space.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国人关注太空</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——如果西方将北京视为伙伴，而不是异类，那么北京也就不太可能会寻求太空霸权</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《连线》杂志：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.wired.com/dangerroom/2011/08/chinas-new-weapons-of-doom/?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+wired%2Findex+%28Wired%3A+Index+3+%28Top+Stories+2%29%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">五角大楼对中国的军力增长并不在乎</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——在新出版的中国军力报告中，美方称中国的目标是“地区性”军事实力。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《洛杉矶时报》：五角大楼发布报告称，</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.latimes.com/news/nationworld/world/la-fg-china-military-20110825,0,4831402.story\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国军队正在着力缩小与美国及其盟国的军事技术差距</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">；然而几项重要的新武器系统尚待时日，尤其是现代航母</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/08/25/world/25military.html?partner=rssnyt&#038;emc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美国官员对中国的军事增长发出警告</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——美国防部长东亚事务助理称中国军力扩充有可能造成太平洋地区不稳定</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/chinarealtime/2011/08/25/china-gets-needlessly-defensive-over-famine-in-africa/?mod=WSJBlog\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国为非洲的饥荒自辩</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——德国外交官称中国大量购买非洲土地加剧了非洲饥荒。中国发言人回应：胡扯！</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20110825/ap_on_bi_ge/as_china_france\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">萨克奇呼吁中国帮助重建自由的利比亚</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——他告诉记者，胡锦涛对欧元地区的情况并不担心</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/environment/2011/aug/25/us-diplomat-china-tiger-farm\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美国外交官化妆成韩国游客暗访中国熊虎饲养场</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——维基解密新披露的电报中，记载了这个故事</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《环球邮报》：一份维基解密显示，美驻加大使馆评估，</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/politics/canadian-diplomatic-trips-to-china-accomplished-little-us-ambassador-says/article2139940/?utm_medium=Feeds:+RSS/Atom&#038;utm_source=Asia-Pacific&#038;utm_content=2139940\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">虽然加拿大外交官在</span>2007<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年间访问中国，但这些访问并未给加拿大带来明显利益</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《环球邮报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/world/asia-pacific/state-investigation-finds-thousands-of-civilian-bodies-in-kashmir-valley/article2140997/?utm_medium=Feeds:+RSS/Atom&#038;utm_source=Asia-Pacific&#038;utm_content=2140997\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">查谟克什米尔邦人权委员会在克什米尔山谷发现至少</span>2156<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">具无名尸体</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，据信是</span></span><span><span>1989</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年起义中印度安全部队所为</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交政策》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.foreignpolicy.com/articles/2011/08/23/all_points_bulletin_qaddafis_on_the_loose\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">卡扎菲家族</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">谱</span></a></span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《经济学人》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.economist.com/node/21526913\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">对冲中国</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">？——对金正日出国访问的评论</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【经济金融】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">卡内基基金会：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.carnegieendowment.org/publications/index.cfm?fa=view&#038;id=45408&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+carnegie%2Fchina+%28DC+-+Region+-+China%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">对中国经济的误解</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——看衰中国经济前景的人，通常以消费占</span></span><span><span>GDP</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">比例过低和投资占</span></span><span><span>GDP</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">比例过高为理由。但这两个数字都是靠不住的。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《今日美国》：</span></span><span><span>“<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.usatoday.com/money/world/story/2011-08-24/Buy-Made-in-China-goods-Benefits-to-US-may-surprise-you/50127452/1\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国制造</span>”<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">商品惠及美国。复杂的中美贸易后面给美国带来益处多多</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/08/25/business/global/chasing-rare-earths-foreign-companies-expand-in-china.html?partner=rssnyt&#038;emc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国利用稀土垄断地位，诱使外国公司在华扩张产能</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">商业内幕：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessinsider.com/the-bank-of-china-is-now-too-big-to-fail-2011-8?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+businessinsider+%28Business+Insider%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国银行“大到不会垮</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">”——尽管中行不是中国最大的银行，但是其国际影响却是无其它中资银行能比的</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/chinarealtime/2011/08/25/eight-questions-living-in-chinas-shadow/?mod=WSJBlog\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">对《生活在中国经济支配的阴影里》一书作者的访谈</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/08/25/opinion/americas-sweatshop-diplomacy.html?_r=1&#038;src=tp\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美国的血汗工厂外交</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——本为吸引访问学者而设立的</span></span><span><span>J-1</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">签证，现在却沦为招募暑期廉价劳工的工具。每年有</span></span><span><span>10</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">万全球大学生花钱到美国来打工，只挣极其微薄的薪水</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><b><span> </span></b></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【生活百态】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国见红博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://seeingredinchina.com/2011/08/25/the-education-g